Version 0.04 -12 May 2006

* Experimental Build.PL as an alternative to make
* Multiple selections allowed 
* Test output (stdout and stderr) is now displayed in the error window

Version 0.03 - 03 Nov 2005

* Background color of progress bar now changes to red/green
* New state "undecided" for tests
* Bulgarian translation
* Multiple test suites can be loaded and executed at once
* Test suites can now be reloaded, so that changes are immediately visible
  in the tree view
* Test suites are now always loaded in subprocesses

Version 0.02 - 27 Oct 2005

* Some toolbar buttons did not work because they triggered
  the wrong callback

Version 0.01 - 26 Oct 2005

* First version
